Introduction

Jessica is a Chinese singer under SW Entertaiment and member of the girl group UDTT. Prior to this, she made her solo debut on July 17, 2022, with the digital single "Midsummer Night's Dream".

Best known for participating in PI Corporation's and Makestar's survival show TIME TURNER, she ranked 3rd place, securing her spot as a member of the final group, I.MET.U. However, on January 17, 2025, Yuting announced her departure from I.MET.U prior to the debut.

Later that year, on February 9th, it was revealed that she would be joining MOAI Entertainment's upcoming girl group E11iVyn. On March 19th, a version of their lineup reveal photo was posted with Lu Yuting having been edited out, suggesting her departure from the group. She later confirmed that she wouldn't be debuting with them due to the CEO's decision. In April, she was revealed to be a member of the upcoming girl group UDTT under the stage name Jessica.
